            "title": "廣汽集團6月汽車銷量跌8.2%",
            "description": "<p>廣汽集團(<a target='_blank' href='https://stock360.hkej.com/quotePlus/02238' >02238</a>)公布，6月汽車產量15.33萬輛，按年跌10.05%；汽車銷量15.01萬輛，下跌8.22%。</p>\n<p>今年上半年，汽車產量80.17萬輛，按年跌6.73%；銷量75.53萬輛，按年下降12.48%。</p>   </div>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"hkej_hkex_notice_dl_btn_2014\">\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2025/0704/2025070401425_c.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">下載港交所通告原文</a>\n</div>\n        ",
